quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  17,105,"Wabilhaqqi anzalnahuwabilhaqqi nazala wama arsalnaka illamubashshiran wanatheera"
  17,106,"Waqur-anan faraqnahulitaqraahu AAala annasi AAalamukthin wanazzalnahu tanzeela"
  17,107,"Qul aminoo bihi aw latu/minoo inna allatheena ootoo alAAilma min qablihi ithayutla AAalayhim yakhirroona lil-athqanisujjada"
  17,108,"Wayaqooloona subhana rabbinain kana waAAdu rabbina lamafAAoola"
  17,109,"Wayakhirroona lil-athqaniyabkoona wayazeeduhum khushooAAa"
  17,110,"Quli odAAoo Allaha awi odAAoo arrahmanaayyan ma tadAAoo falahu al-asmao alhusnawala tajhar bisalatika wala tukhafitbiha wabtaghi bayna thalika sabeela"
  17,111,"Waquli alhamdu lillahi allatheelam yattakhith waladan walam yakun lahu shareekun feealmulki walam yakun lahu waliyyun mina aththulliwakabbirhu takbeera"
  18,1,"Alhamdu lillahi allatheeanzala AAala AAabdihi alkitaba walam yajAAal lahuAAiwaja"
  18,2,"Qayyiman liyunthira ba/san shadeedanmin ladunhu wayubashshira almu/mineena allatheenayaAAmaloona assalihati anna lahum ajran hasana"
  18,3,"Makitheena feehi abada"
  18,4,"Wayunthira allatheena qalooittakhatha Allahu walada"
